{"tid":1536773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［問劇情］想問下肯開戰未？","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:05:56.000Z","uid":58161,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cf17e2407152f6e6fd5011b9dbe3b27716b08f","tid":1536773,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"最近有套劇集睇到我又緊張又心痛，好似叫光乜乜乜<br />\n我睇到而家劇情就係軍政府大撚曬，市民啲火谷到恆<br />\n但係始終未有真正既武力升級對抗軍政府<br />\n我知大部分義士可能未覺醒，未衝破心理關口<br />\n但可唔可以為左咁耐以黎犧牲既偉大傷者 鼓起勇氣？<br />\n<br />\n我知，套劇集播左幾個月，每位義士都keep住反思進步<br />\n我知，而家啲警犬連行街食飯都可以話你襲警<br />\n但我真係好想睇到啲警犬仆街既一日<br />\n<br />\n我希望每次對付落單警犬，都唔好再有人阻住曬叫唔好打，你要叫唔該行開一二邊叫<br />\n同埋我知街坊真係純粹落街散步，但下次可唔可以順手拎啲唔要既垃圾落街大大力掉左佢 至於掉去邊到......<br />\n仲有就係救手足！每次睇電視見到前面既人拎曬鐵枝長棍，但好多時最後都只係拎住佢向後跑，多三四個人留低，或者就可以救返手足一命<br />\n<br />\n最後，我希望所有傷者，無論生理定心理創傷，都快啲康復！<br />\n已犧牲既偉大烈士，我地永遠都會記得你地！<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"992542be82c0c2f5ca53f685532fe4988731b67c","tid":1536773,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9560458db71fcab2d53c45f264d49832bcff6c7a","tid":1536773,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:24.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"3397629bbd5110a63639a45251836df3350a554d","tid":1536773,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:37.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"04845e051c538caa1f41601152a487a1d2a84f79","tid":1536773,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"5498df73d5f446dd1de6535c29a2de574b49eabb","tid":1536773,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:59.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"579d0b4c28ded98f874212bd9744eea80bbf12e5","tid":1536773,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"我每個post 都會咒一次：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警全家變植物人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) <br />\n908 九月八日 2:00pm <br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》集會請願 ! ! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯國旗!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">唱國歌 !</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCGOYms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGOYms.jpg&h=ced74507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<i